## How to work in this repo

This project is run by the `prompt-to-production` skill (https://skills.sh/...). The skill is autonomous after Stage A:

1. On a fresh session, read this file.
2. Read `LOG.md`'s last entry. That tells you where to resume.
3. Read `NOTES-TO-ADMIN.md` — any unresolved BLOCKER affecting the current phase pauses that phase. Continue with non-dependent work where possible.
4. Pick up the next concrete task. Execute. Test. Update `LOG.md`. Continue until done, blocked, or context-exhausted.

If you are a human reading this, the same orientation applies — but you may also want to read `VISION.md` and `PRODUCT-SPEC.md` for the full picture.

